  "response": "Happiness is a complex and multifaceted emotional state that typically encompasses feelings of joy, contentment, and overall satisfaction with life. It can be experienced both as a temporary mood or a more enduring state of being. Factors contributing to happiness can vary widely among individuals, including relationships, achievements, personal values, health, and even genetic predisposition. Philosophers, psychologists, and other researchers have explored happiness extensively, but it ultimately remains a subjective experience that each person may understand and pursue in their unique way.",
